Package: ppindices
Title: Phenotypic Plasticity Indices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Benedikt", "Haarscheidt", email = "benedikt.haarscheidt@yahoo.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of implementations for quantifying phenotypic plasticity from
    reaction-norm data. Provides functions to compute a broad range of plasticity indices
    from trait values measured across environments.
